    • getMetaTagContent

      public String[] getMetaTagContent(String attribute, String attributeValue)
      Retrieves the "content" of the meta tags for a key pair attribute-attributeValue. <code> <meta name="robots" content="index" /> <meta name="robots" content="follow" /> <meta http-equiv="Expires" content="now" /> </code> this can be used like this <code> getMetaTagContent("name","robots") will return { "index","follow" } getMetaTagContent("http-equiv","Expires") will return { "now" } </code>
